<text top="115" left="210" width="275" height="13" font="0">the  Office  of  the  United  Nations  High  Commissioner  for  Human </text>
<text top="127" left="113" width="371" height="13" font="0">Rights  to  provide  the  working  group  with  the  assistance  necessary  for  it  to  fulfil  its </text>
<text top="139" left="113" width="39" height="13" font="0">mandate; </text>
